lex Robertshaw 和 Tom AD Fuller 制作，他们的共同笔名是 Kaines &amp; Tom AD。它定于 3 月 1 日发布，您可以在这里预购。</p><p>去年， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/everything-everything-on-their-apocalyptic-new-album-i-cant-see-much-good-in-the-future-3525605">Everything Everything 与<em>NME</em>谈论了即将发行的 LP</a> ，并透露了其背后的动机。 </p><figure id="attachment_3523556" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3523556" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3523556" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/everything-everything-Mountainhead-album-art.jpg" alt="一切一切“Mountainhead”专辑封面" width="2000" height="2000" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/everything-everything-Mountainhead-album-art.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/everything-everything-Mountainhead-album-art-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/everything-everything-Mountainhead-album-art-400x400.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/everything-everything-Mountainhead-album-art-800x800.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/everything-everything-Mountainhead-album-art-696x696.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/everything-everything-Mountainhead-album-art-1392x1392.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/everything-everything-Mountainhead-album-art-1068x1068.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3523556" class="wp-caption-text">一切一切“Mountainhead”专辑封面。图片来源：新闻界</figcaption></figure><p>“这并不是一次伟大的旅程和斗争，”希格斯告诉<em>《NME》</em> 。</p><p> “我们希望在时间上尽快回到正轨，因为就大流行而言，我们处于一个奇怪的境地。我们总是在错误的时间发行专辑，错过了音乐节。我们确实需要回到原计划，我们已经有了在“Raw Data Feel”巡演期间一直在研究的想法，所以我们只是做了我们该做的事情，很快就把唱片放在一起。”</p><p>在其他消息中，乐队将于<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/everything-everything-share-new-single-cold-reactor-and-more-details-of-album-mountainhead-3523541">下个月开始英国巡演</a>。请参阅<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music