com/artists/kenny-beats">Kenny Beats</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/beadbadoobee">Beabadoobee</a> 、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kenya-grace">肯尼亚·格雷斯</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nia-archives">尼亚档案馆</a>、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/two-door-cinema-club">两门电影俱乐部</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Neck-Deep">Neck Deep</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-wombats">The Wombats</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/Ashnikko">Ashnikko</a> 、David Kushner、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/rachel-chinouriri">Rachel Cinouriri</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/hak-baker">Hak Baker</a> 、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-last-dinner-party">最后的晚宴</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sonny-fodera">Sonny Fodera</a>等。</p><p>周六在雷丁，“Born To Die”歌手、DJ 兼制作人 Fred Again 等人将成为英国独家亮相的头条新闻。在门票全部售完的阅读日，<a href="/artists/raye">雷伊 (Raye</a> )、露天看台<a href="/artists/bleachers">(Bleachers</a> )、<a href="/artists/courting">求爱 (Courting</a> )、最后的晚宴 (The Last Evening Party) 等剧目也将上演。</p><p>弗雷德再次......将创造雷丁和利兹的历史，成为第一位关闭著名主舞台的电子艺术家，并将其命名为“我明年参加的唯一英国音乐节，也是我参加的第一个音乐节。”</p><p>音乐节<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/reading-leeds-2024-festival-confirm-day-splits-and-whos-headlining-when-3548999">此前公布了演出时间</a>，并确认<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/LIAM-GALLAGHER">Liam Gallagher</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/catfish-and-the-bottlemen">Catfish &amp; The Bottlemen</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/skrillex">Skrillex</a>将于周五在利兹演出，周日在雷丁演出。 </p><figure id="attachment_3580759" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3580759" style="width: 2300px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3580759" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Reading-Leeds-Poster.-Credit-PRESS.jpg" alt="阅读和利兹海报。信用：新闻。" width="2300" height="2875" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Reading-Leeds-Poster.-Credit-PRESS.jpg 2300w, https://www.nme.com/wp-con