m/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/usher-pharrell-diddy-jay-z-@-2000-x-1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/usher-pharrell-diddy-jay-z-@-2000-x-1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/usher-pharrell-diddy-jay-z-@-2000-x-1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/usher-pharrell-diddy-jay-z-@-2000-x-1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/usher-pharrell-diddy-jay-z-@-2000-x-1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/usher-pharrell-diddy-jay-z-@-2000-x-1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artists/usher">亚瑟小子</a>透露，他本应与<a href="/artists/jay-z">Jay-Z</a> 、<a href="/artists/pharrell-williams">法瑞尔·威廉姆斯</a>和<a href="/artists/diddy">吹牛老爹</a>组成一个超级组合，但从未实现。</p><p>本周，亚瑟小子出现在由前美国足球运动员香农·夏普主持的热门<a href="https://youtu.be/Fa0jhYh3nhE" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Club Shay Shay</em></a>播客中。夏普问道：“是啊！”歌手是否曾经拒绝过后来后悔的合作。</p><p> “你会因为这个而恨我的，”亚瑟回答道。 “Jay-Z、 <a href="/artists/pharrell">Pharrell</a> 、Diddy 和我本来应该是一个组合。是的，那太疯狂了。我没有说“不”。我没有说：“是的。”我想我们只是陷入了困境。我们都陷入了这一刻。我们正在讨论这个问题，并召开了秘密会议。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C2yYR-uMvWi/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div>